The paper deals with a large-scale dataset of "What if..." questions over procedural text, which involves natural language processing, machine learning, and reasoning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
